神之餘仲要聽老細閒言閒語"},{"pid":"4908f83d200c043e9035f8721ad590499543548e","tid":129024,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"有咩工有公司私家車接送?<br />\n成日落site要行好遠去搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2450c4fa3043b1f2de99affe54e4b3eb1c33cea","tid":129024,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f8c4903e534adaf5e084fb3c7e4396b37e2c5c6","tid":129024,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"公司董事"},{"pid":"5cfce596405d182ef0c6dac3efdf430c3b0bee7f","tid":129024,"uid":26353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:50:30.000Z","msg":"點心呀姐"},{"pid":"bb8964430196106cc10b0ad955c3798073c0d957","tid":129024,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點心呀姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859d7a43897f3d3e433a90086da5bc95c76ac56b","tid":129024,"uid":70598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點心呀姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470680d87bb73c1df585014a3cfb562728350aa9","tid":129024,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點心呀姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class